targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  creationtime AS "time",
  gasprice
FROM transactions
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(creationtime)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(creationtime,$__interval),
  code AS "Code",
  max(requestkey) AS "Request Key",
  max(chainid) AS "Chain ID"
FROM transactions
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(creationtime) AND
  code != '0'
GROUP BY 1, code
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
floor(extract(epoch from creationtime)/60)*60 AS "time",
(MAX(115792089237316195423570985008687907853269984665640564039457584007913129639935 / blocks.target)/30) AS "Chain 0"
FROM blocks
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(creationtime) AND
  chainid = 0
GROUP BY 
         blocks.creationtime,
         blocks.target
ORDER BY 1
